rows.label: tlk70000061_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I believe that naming something is
one's way of giving meaning to it.

rows.label: tlk70000061_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I only wish I could name the rush
of incredible feelings that have
been welling up within me...

rows.label: tlk70000061_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Not to mention naming all the
places and happenings that we
come across on our adventures.

rows.label: tlk70000061_02_msg0004
rows.name:
So that each and every one will
stand as a reminder of the time
I've spent with Rita...
